coza.opencollab.synthesis.push.dbo

Class Push

  • java.lang.Object
    • coza.opencollab.synthesis.push.dbo.Push
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class Push
extends Object
implements Serializable
    A class representing a Push Notification message. A single push notification instance is shared for many users and devices. The PushDeviceTuple class represent the status of a push message being sent to a device.
    See Also:
